    "content": "<@412614104222531604> Is there a way to ensure in the Kurtosis config that the spammor only submits blobs tx to a specific client ?",
    "created_at": "2026-05-11T09:52:46.597000+00:00",
    "attachments": []
  },
  {
    "author": "aarshshahoffchain",
    "category": "Consensus Layer",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "My current spammor config is:\n\n\"\"\"\nspamoor_params:\n  image: ethpandaops/spamoor:master\n  max_mem: 4000\n  spammers:\n    - scenario: eoatx\n      config:\n        throughput: 200\n    - scenario: blobs\n      config:\n        throughput: 20\n\"\"\"",
    "created_at": "2026-05-11T09:52:59.152000+00:00",
    "attachments": []
  },
  {
    "author": "barnabasbusa",
    "category": "Consensus Layer",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "yeah",
    "created_at": "2026-05-11T09:53:02.220000+00:00",
    "attachments": []
  },
  {
    "author": "barnabasbusa",
    "category": "Consensus Layer",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "you can do `client_group`",
    "created_at": "2026-05-11T09:53:36.660000+00:00",
    "attachments": []
  },
  {
    "author": "aarshshahoffchain",
    "category": "Consensus Layer",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "Can you help me with a sample config please ?",
    "created_at": "2026-05-11T09:53:49.752000+00:00",
    "attachments": []
  },
  {
    "author": "barnabasbusa",
    "category": "Consensus Layer",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "```\nspamoor_params:\n  image: ethpandaops/spamoor:master\n  spammers:\n    - scenario: eoatx\n      config:\n        throughput: 100\n        client_group: prysm-geth-1\n```",
    "created_at": "2026-05-11T09:54:19.805000+00:00",
    "attachments": []
